column5: Im just asking a question here. I have noticed that the local Ford dealer has been getting more and more F150,s with the logo Cabelas on the box of thier trucks. Could it be a promo for whats to come,or are all ford dealers getting them?
Sorry mang....do a google search for "cabela's ford f-150"...looks like they do it as a package on their trucks.  But OH how sweet would that be...Barrie needs one!!  Let's start a petition
thats not the first time ive heard of this...
NO.....this can NOT happen until all of us USA boys are taken care of......
Well with the Park Place,I can see it happening.Give that Vaughan Mill a run for thier money.       Hey,we gave you Timmies.Heck they are even the Bills biggest sponsor.HAHAHAHAHAHAHA
Well, you got me by the short hairs there........Timmy does make a he!! of a cup of coffee.......
Sounds similar to the old "Eddie Bauer" packages they used to put out. It would be a nice thought though to open one in Barrie!
